{"tid":2394891,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大建設附屬學校 打造粵港澳國際教育示範區","createTime":"2021-02-04T13:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T07:49:15.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62f22512f0ff92cbac7fa0e02c02803f2092fb3e","tid":2394891,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"1月29日，龍崗區古董打造粵港澳國際教育示範區啟動儀式，並解讀《深圳市龍崗區打造粵港澳國際教育示範區的實施方案（2021-2025）》。會上，龍崗區政府與香港中文大學（深圳）長期合作辦學協議，雙方將合作建設香港中文大學（深圳）附屬學校。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.jiemian.com/article/5617654.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.jiemian.com%2Farticle%2F5617654.html&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=e3ed4e36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.jiemian.com/article/5617654.html</a>"},{"pid":"d77d56e42ca7265f49d9b3d9dca43b728a3e1f5e","tid":2394891,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Proud of my school"},{"pid":"6339a60742b81f31e0d56dc7a6b46d7c47465b72","tid":2394891,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e428c84fb979c5513b0c658b55c8bfeeeea13841","tid":2394891,"uid":248232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"支大好黃㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad04913d28a6e3698fa9f167cbb8af63956980c","tid":2394891,"uid":68903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:36:24.000Z","msg":"中大個名咁響都有敢讀?"},{"pid":"9984272e3d5cbf52065bc356a9e875eb6e8a6574","tid":2394891,"uid":136216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"個件段狗所以連中大學生都拉&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"6747c82ffb037c22e13b3a00eadbf3bef554cb79","tid":2394891,"uid":74310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc